#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Accounting App</b>: </strong>Keep track of the organization's "
"budget, managing expenses and income\n"
"                    from fees and fundraising.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>Application Comptabilité</b> : </strong>suivez le budget de "
"l’organisation, gérez les dépenses et les revenus issus des cotisations et "
"des collectes de fonds.<br/>"

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Email Marketing App</b>: </strong>Engage the student body with "
"newsletters about upcoming events,\n"
"                    elections, and important announcements.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>Application E-mail Marketing</b> : </strong>impliquez les "
"étudiants avec des newsletters sur les événements à venir, les élections et "
"les annonces importantes.<br/>"

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Events App</b>:</strong> Create and promote student events, "
"handling registrations and ticket sales\n"
"                    online for everything from galas to workshops.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>Application Événements</b> :</strong> créez et promouvez des "
"événements étudiants, gérez les inscriptions et la vente de billets en "
"ligne, qu’il s’agisse de galas ou d’ateliers.<br/>"

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Members App</b>: </strong>Manage your membership base "
"efficiently, tracking active status, dues\n"
"                    payments, and renewal dates.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>Application Membres</b> : </strong>gérez efficacement votre base "
"de membres, suivez le statut actif, les paiements de cotisations et les "
"dates de renouvellement.<br/>"

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Website App</b>: </strong>Build a portal for your organization to "
"share news, host a calendar, and\n"
"                    allow members to sign up for activities.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>Application Site Web</b> : </strong>créez un portail pour votre "
"organisation afin de partager des actualités, héberger un agenda et "
"permettre aux membres de s’inscrire aux activités.<br/>"

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>eCommerce App</b>:</strong> Sell branded merchandise, event kits, "
"or study materials directly to your\n"
"                    members online."
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>Application eCommerce</b> :</strong> vendez des articles de "
"marque, des kits d’événement ou du matériel d’étude directement à vos "
"membres en ligne."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:event.event,description:student_organization.event_event_2
msgid "<strong>A Night to Remember – Celebrate, Connect, and Shine</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Une soirée inoubliable – Célébrez, échangez et brillez</strong>"

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Automate reminders.</strong> SMS or email nudges cut no‑shows and\n"
"                            keep vaccinations on schedule."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Automatisez les rappels.</strong> Les rappels par SMS ou par e-mail "
"réduisent les rendez-vous manqués et permettent de maintenir les "
"vaccinations à jour."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Dashboards</strong>: Create a visual overview of memberships, "
"ticket\n"
"                    sales, merchandise, and engagement stats."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Tableaux de bord</strong> : créez une vue d’ensemble visuelle des "
"adhésions, des ventes de billets, des articles dérivés et des statistiques "
"d’engagement."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Documents</strong>: Store meeting notes, budgets, and reports in "
"one\n"
"                    place — no more chasing files."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Documents</strong> : stockez les comptes rendus de réunions, les "
"budgets et les rapports au même endroit — plus besoin de rechercher des "
"fichiers."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Email Marketing</strong>: Build campaigns with drag-and-drop "
"templates,\n"
"                    track opens and clicks."
msgstr ""
"<strong>E-mail Marketing</strong> : créez des campagnes avec des modèles en "
"glisser-déposer, suivez les ouvertures et les clics."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Events</strong>: Configure events, assign ticket types, and track\n"
"                    attendance."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Événements</strong> : configurez des événements, attribuez des types "
"de billets et suivez les présences."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Expenses</strong>: Upload receipts, categorize spending, and follow "
"approval\n"
"            steps."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Dépenses</strong> : ajoutez des reçus, catégorisez les dépenses et "
"suivez les étapes d’approbation."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Experiment ! </strong>Did you know you can create a copy of your\n"
"                            database to try things out ? Simply go to"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Expérimentez ! </strong>Saviez-vous que vous pouvez créer une copie "
"de votre base de données pour effectuer des tests ? Il vous suffit d’aller "
"dans"

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Knowledge</strong>: Share how-tos, onboarding guides, and policies "
"with\n"
"                    new members and committees."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Connaissances</strong> : partagez des guides pratiques, des guides "
"d’intégration et des politiques avec les nouveaux membres et les comités."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Membership</strong>: Automatically link a sold membership to a "
"customer\n"
"                    profile."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Membres</strong> : liez automatiquement une adhésion vendue à un "
"profil client."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Planning</strong>: Use planning to manage shifts at your events, "
"keep\n"
"                    everyone updated on everyone's whereabouts."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Planification</strong> : utilisez la planification pour gérer les "
"équipes lors de vos événements, tenez tout le monde informé de l’emplacement "
"de chacun."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Point of Sale</strong>: Also possible to sell memberships physically "
"at\n"
"                    booths or events."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Point de vente</strong> : vendez également des adhésions sur place, "
"lors de stands ou d’événements."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Point of Sale</strong>: Sell tickets at the register through the "
"point of\n"
"                    sale, assign them to your contacts."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Point de Vente</strong> : vendez des billets à la caisse via le "
"point de vente, attribuez-les à vos contacts."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Project Dashboard</strong>: keep track of all invoices, expenses,\n"
"                    budgets, and more using the projects dashboards."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Tableau de bord Projet</strong> : suivez toutes les factures, "
"dépenses, budgets et plus encore grâce aux tableaux de bord des projets."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Projects</strong>: Break large initiatives into tasks, track "
"deadlines,\n"
"                    assign roles."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Projets</strong> : décomposez les projets d’envergure en tâches, "
"suivez les échéances et attribuez les rôles."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Sales</strong>: Ticket revenue flows into your standard accounting "
"flow."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Ventes</strong> : les revenus des billets sont intégrés dans votre "
"flux comptable standard."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Sales</strong>: Use price lists to offer exclusive discounts to "
"active\n"
"                    members."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Ventes</strong> : utilisez des listes de prix pour offrir des "
"remises exclusives aux membres actifs."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Social Marketing</strong>: Schedule and publish posts across "
"multiple\n"
"                    platforms (Instagram, LinkedIn, X)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Social Marketing</strong> : planifiez et publiez des publications "
"sur plusieurs plateformes (Instagram, LinkedIn, X)."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Start small, iterate.</strong> Configure your website and\n"
"                            appointments first, then add your products to "
"the mix, before managing\n"
"                            your consultations."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Commencez progressivement, ajustez.</strong> Configurez d’abord "
"votre site web et vos rendez-vous, puis ajoutez vos produits avant de gérer "
"vos consultations."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:student_organization.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Tasks</strong>: View progress in Kanban or Gantt formats for clarity."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Tâches</strong> : visualisez la progression en formats Kanban ou "
"Gantt pour plus de clarté."

